# IoT Digital Twin Systems for Smart Agriculture
> AWS-powered IoT sensor networks with digital twin visualization for precision agriculture monitoring

âš ï¸ **Note:** This repository documents research conducted at BMS College of Engineering from 2023-2026, resulting in two published papers. Code samples and architecture diagrams are provided; full datasets are not included due to academic IP considerations.

## ğŸ“š Published Research

**1. Exploring Digital Twins for Plant Growth Monitoring** (2023)  
*7th International Conference on Computation System and Information Technology for Sustainable Solutions (CSITSS)*  
